   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[- - - whenever] you so announce [I shall restore it to you without any] delay or excuse [in accordance with the] law of [deposits] according [as has been written above] and you, the above mentioned Gerontios, shall have the [right of execution upon me, the] acknowledging party, and upon [all my] property, as in accordance with a legal decision and having been asked the formal question [I have assented. I, Aurelius] Aion, the afore mentioned, acknowledge [as has been written above. - - -]</ab>
         </div>
